<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAIBAL I TLAIH CH194</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Baibal cauk cu thlah lo in i tlaih ko, A sungmi a cawnpiaknak thlau
 hna hlah, A itmi nunnak kha a tun thawh than hna, Thih hnu nunnak kong
 biakam a fehter.

[C1]
   Baibal kha i tlaih, Baibal kha i tlaih, Kan mei inn le lam hruaitu,
   Baibal kha.

[V2]
 Lungvar man sung Baibal kha i tlaih zungzal, Tlu ril a thawh, nun
 hmunhnak a pek hna, A sunlawinak kong kan chim cawk bal lai lo; Caan um
 lioah a thluachuahnak kawl tuah.

[C2]
   Baibal kha i tlaih, Baibal kha i tlaih, Kan mei inn le lam hruaitu,
   Baibal kha.

[V3]
 Kephau caan kipah ceunak mei inn a si, Tlu ril lo-in, seino mi a hruai
 hna, A lotlaumi nunnak ruahchannak a pek; Tar ca thiangthunh Ca uk tha
 bik a si.

[C3]
   Baibal kha i tlaih, Baibal kha i tlaih, Kan mei inn le lam hruaitu,
   Baibal kha.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>194</hymn_number>
</song>